    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014I've taken great care of it and it runs like a dream! It's super reliable and still looks great on the road, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend trips. I'm sad to see it go, but it's ready for its next adventure. Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
