    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s example featuring the celebrated S54 3.2L inline-six engine. The powerplant retains its signature high-revving character, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double VANOS to deliver linear torque across the rev range. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. To ensure structural longevity, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the VANOS system has been professionally serviced. The chassis remains sharp, benefitting from refreshed bushings and a well-sorted suspension geometry that minimizes body roll. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals and drivetrain synchronization are dialed in for peak performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
