    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained luxury sedan offers a refined driving experience and a professional aesthetic. The exterior is finished in a deep Obsidian Black that still holds a deep, mirror-like shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the lower front valance consistent with highway commuting, the body is straight and free of any significant dings. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of premium charcoal leather and brushed aluminum accents. The upholstery is in excellent shape, showing only light softening on the driver's side bolster. All technology, from the adaptive cruise control to the premium 12-speaker audio system, operates exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized centers, with the most recent oil service and multi-point inspection completed just last month. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is an honest, reliable vehicle for a buyer who appreciates a car that has been treated with respect and diligence. Includes a full set of weather-mats, two key fobs, and a comprehensive binder of service receipts.",
